timing_report_...mary_at_bottom(25.10)  timing_report_...mary_at_bottom(25.10)

Name
       timing_report_enable_slack_summary_at_bottom

Syntax
       timing_report_enable_slack_summary_at_bottom {true | false}

       Default: false

       Prints  additional  time  details, such as, Required time, Arrival, and
       Slack, at the bottom of the timing report. For example,

       Req Time = 0.262  (-3.00S) | 0.544  | 0.094 | 0.141

       Arr Time = 2.238  (+3.00S) | 1.774  | 0.155 | 0.131

       Slk Time = -1.773 (-3.00S) | -1.230 | 0.181 | 0.181

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

